    ///
    /// We say that a key-value pair `e :: (K, V)` is an **entry** in the map `map` if and only if
    ///
    /// ```text
    ///  e :: (K, V). e  map  ( i  [0, map.len()). map[i] = e).
    /// ```
    ///
    /// The set of **keys** in the map `map` is defined as
    ///
    /// ```text
    /// keys(map) := { k :: K |  i  [0, map.len()). map[i].key() = k }
    /// ```
    ///
