    /// Note that multiset equality is not needed here because every key is unique in an index map.
    ///
    /// The index map `map` is **sorted** with respect to its keys if
    ///
    /// ```text
    /// is_sorted(map) :=  i  [0, map.len() - 1). map[i].key()  map[i + 1].key().
    /// ```
