    /// and `e2` be entries in `self`. Then `e1.key() <= e2.key()` if and only if
    /// `e1.index() <= e2.index()`. More precisely, given the index map `self`
    ///
    /// ```text
    /// forall e1, e2 in self. e1.index() <= e2.index() <-> e1.key() <= e2.key()
    /// ```
