    ///
    /// ```text
    /// forall i1, i2 in [0, self.len()). forall k1, k2 :: K. forall v1, v2 :: V.
    /// (i1, (k1, v1)), (i2, (k2, v2)) in self --> i1 <= i2 <-> k1 <= k2.
    /// ```
    ///
    /// Otherwise, the index map is in **unsorted order by key**, or is **unsorted** for short.
    ///
